[DQC.US.0181.10182] The concept InterestExpense is a descendant of OperatingExpenses. The element OperatingExpenses represents operating expenses. The element InterestExpense represents non operating interest and should not be included as a calculation component of OperatingExpenses. Select the operating interest expense element InterestExpenseOperating instead of InterestExpense.
